        "text": "A high school teacher, Rainer Wenger, comes up with an experiment\n\nin order to explain to his students how totalitarian governments work.\n\nAs their leader he asks the students to call him Mr Wegner, chooses\n\nthe motto, creates a logo and names the group “The Wave” adding\n\na secret sign. A role-playing game with tragic results begins. Within\n\na few days, what began with harmless notions like discipline and\n\ncommunity builds into a real movement that soon erupts into violence.\n\nThe teacher decides to break off the experiment but it’s too late: the\n\nwave is out of control."
